    <string name="quick_guide">Set up your own contact information from the settings menu.\n\n
    BarCodeKey creates a QR code that consists of your information and a public encryption key.\n\n
    Use the "Scan" button to read a QR code from your friend\'s BarCodeKey device.\n\n
    You can reset your encryption keys from the settings by pressing the "Reset keys" button.\n\n
    Reset your encryption keys only when it is absolutely necessary, since the old key you
    might have shared to your friends turns obsolete!</string>
